description.narrative: The Project Development Objective is to support flood recovery as well as future oriented risk reduction efforts of the GoB through: (i) reconstruction of damaged houses and road infrastructure; (ii) strengthening the flood management capacity in Kosi Basin; (iii) enhancing livelihood opportunities of the affected people; and, (iv) improving the emergency response capacity for future disasters.
